      "category": "ai",
      "title": "LeRobot v0.6.0: Imagine, Evaluate, Improve",
      "url": "https://huggingface.co/blog/lerobot-release-v060",
      "discuss_url": "https://huggingface.co/blog/lerobot-release-v060",
      "score": null,
      "comments": null,
      "author": null,
      "published": "2026-07-07T00:00:00Z",
      "bullets": [
        "Hugging Face LeRobot v0.6.0 advances PyTorch-based robotics with enhanced simulation, policy evaluation, and imitation learning workflows.",
        "The release improves integration with simulated environments like MuJoCo and Gym for evaluating robotic policies like ACT and Diffusion Policy.",
        "Practitioners can train neural network policies on Hugging Face datasets, benchmark them in simulation, and deploy to physical hardware like Aloha."
      ]
    },
    {
      "source": "lobsters",
      "subsource": "lobste.rs/programming",
      "category": "engineering",
      "title": "Jam Programming Language",
      "url": "https://rapha.land/jam-programming-language/",
