      "score": 33,
      "comments": 20,
      "author": "bittermandel",
      "published": "2026-07-06T08:22:08Z",
      "bullets": [
        "Features a statically typed, functional design prioritizing robust type inference, algebraic data types, and expressive pattern matching capabilities.",
        "Compiles to highly optimized target code, focusing on low memory overhead and predictable execution speeds without a heavy garbage collector.",
        "Provides built-in tooling for modern dependency management, unit testing, and zero-cost interoperability with existing C-interface APIs."
      ]
    },
